description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Anurak purrs with a rating of 70, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 210, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, Stringalong for East, Leverage for South, and 8 for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/20703-67683-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Anurak [210 Votes, Top 5% Score]
